snippet.title: NEO: The World Ends with You | Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
NEO: The World Ends with You is coming Summer 2021 to PlayStation 4 and Nintendo Switch!

Explore a stylized recreation of Shibuya, as you take on the role of Rindo to battle for survival and unravel the mysteries of the deadly “Reaper’s Game” in this new Action RPG for PlayStation 4 and Nintendo Switch.

For more information, visit https://square-enix-games.com/neotwewy 

Keep up to date with the latest news by following us at:
https://www.instagram.com/SquareEnix  
https://www.twitter.com/SquareEnix
https://www.facebook.com/SquareEnix
#NTWEWY
